      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, ensuring a visceral connection to the M-variable differential lock. This collector-grade example features a reinforced rear subframe, pristine factory-original paint, and an impeccably preserved interior. The suspension maintains its factory-spec damping and bushing integrity, providing the communicative handling and chassis rigidity expected of a showroom-quality machine. Fully documented and mechanically flawless, this is a turn-key investment for the purist.",
